data.description: The one you've been waiting for! This spacious 3 bed 2 bath residence, boasts RV access and is situated in a well-established Camarillo neighborhood close to excellent schools and parks. Upon entry through the double doors, you'll discover an open-concept living area with recessed lighting and wood like flooring. The dining room flows right into the kitchen which showcases custom alder wood cabinets, slate tile floors and leathered black granite countertops. Enjoy an indoor/outdoor feel with Teza bifold panels or relax by the fireplace adorned with a black walnut mantle. Custom shutters dress the windows and the recently remodeled bathrooms add a modern touch. The backyard offers a covered patio with sun shades and a tranquil fountain. Nestled on the side of the house, you have RV access to fit a 28 ft trailer including an RV dump. With numerous features, this home is a must-see!
